## Limitations

The analysis is based on secondary sources and interpretations, which may carry inherent biases. The complexity of the Reformation's impact means that not all perspectives and nuances could be fully explored within this report. Additionally, the focus was primarily on Western Europe, potentially overlooking regional variations in the Reformation's effects.